{
  "name": "Drake Companion: Summon",
  "type": "feat",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">You must have a token on the scene to use this spell (Warpgate mutation limitation).</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Signika, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">You must have an actor called \"CPR - Drake Companion\" in your actors directory. You can enable the \"Keep Summon Actors Updated\" setting to have this happen automatically.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">Enable \"Short / Long Rest Listener\" in the module settings for this to work.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Signika, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">After using this feature a new feature called \"Drake Companion: Command\" will be available in your features.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Signika, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">If you use \"Tidy 5e Sheet\" it will automatically be favorited.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Signika, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">If you use \"Custom Character Sheet Sections\" it will be in it's own section called \"Class Features.\"</span></p><p>You can customize the avatars and tokens for this feature with custom file paths with the Medkit -&gt; Configure.</p><p>Summon Animations by: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/RXwkJD4hTe\">EskieMoh#2969</a></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Signika, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\"><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">This feature is safe to be renamed.</em></span></p>",
